Presidents Cup (Golf)
Ryder Cup (Golf)
lead_paragraph: Jordan Spieth, who won the Hero World Challenge with a tournament-record 26-under-par 262, and Rory McIlroy have gained experience and momentum while Woods has struggled to regain his old form.
